1 at the date of recognition as directed by the Supreme
2 Court;
3 2. The sum of Two Thousand Dollars ($2,000.00) per year,
4 payable monthly, to any official court reporter who is a holds one
5 or more of the following certifications:
6 a. Registered Merit Reporter (RMR), as recognized by the
